net.zerobandwidth.android.lib.services

Interface SimpleServiceConnection.Listener<LS extends android.app.Service>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SingletonServiceTest.FirstContext, SingletonServiceTest.SecondContext, SingletonServiceTest.SingletonServiceTestContext
    Enclosing class:
    SimpleServiceConnection<S extends android.app.Service>

    public static interface SimpleServiceConnection.Listener<LS extends android.app.Service>
    Because connections can take a while, the object that is waiting for the connection to be completed should implement this interface to receive a signal when the connection is established.
    Since:
    zerobandwidth-net/android 0.0.1 (#1)
